==Animation==
In 2004 the Japanese broadcasting company [[NHK|Nippon Hōsō Kyōkai]] turned Poirot and Marple into animated characters in the anime series ''[[Agatha Christie's Great Detectives Poirot and Marple]]'', introducing Mabel West (daughter of Miss Marple's mystery-writer nephew [[Raymond West (character)|Raymond West]], a [[canon (fiction)|canonical]] Christie character) and her duck Oliver as new characters.

